# Accounts Receivable Ageing Analysis

Provide a dedicated ageing section.

## Ageing Buckets

| Bucket            | Amount |
| ----------------- | ------ |
| Current           | R0.00  |
| 1 - 30 Days       | R0.00  |
| 31 - 60 Days      | R0.00  |
| 61+ Days          | R0.00  |
|                   |        |
| Total Outstanding | R0.00  |

---

## Ageing Visualization

Display as:

### Option A (Recommended)

Horizontal stacked progress bar

```text
Current      ██████████
1-30 Days    ████
31-60 Days   ██
61+ Days     █
```

### Option B

Simple doughnut chart showing debt distribution by ageing category.

