# Client Health Score

Provide a calculated client health indicator.

## Excellent

* No overdue invoices
* Pays on time

Green

---

## Good

* Minor overdue balances
* Usually pays on time

Blue

---

## At Risk

* Consistent overdue invoices
* Increasing outstanding balance

Orange

---

## Critical

* Multiple invoices older than 90 days
* Collection action required

Red

---

# Payment Behaviour Analytics

Provide payment performance metrics.

| Metric                  | Description                           |
| ----------------------- | ------------------------------------- |
| Average Days to Pay     | Average time taken to settle invoices |
| Last Payment Date       | Most recent payment                   |
| Largest Payment         | Largest payment received              |
| Total Payments Received | Lifetime payment total                |
| Collection Efficiency   | Paid ÷ Invoiced                       |

